      "May, June and September are the easiest months for warm coast weather, clear bay views and manageable traffic on the Budva-Kotor corridor.",
      "If you are short on time, drop Podgorica to an arrival night and keep the extra day for Kotor or Durmitor instead.",
      "A rental car is most useful for Lovcen and Durmitor, but buses are cheaper and easy enough on the Podgorica-Cetinje-Kotor-Budva coastal spine.",
